## Commenting Format

### Section Comment

```js
// ============================================================================
// Section Title
// Description of what this section handles.
// ============================================================================
```

### Function Comment

```js
// Function: doThing
// Handles X functionality with validation
```

Use `//` only (never `/* */`) and every function must have a one-liner summary.

